  "text": "While we found a strong correlation between osteoblast suppression and HSPC mobilization, our studies do not prove a causal relationship. It is interesting that another stem cell niche was recently identified near endothelial cells [CITATION_1] . While it is temping to speculate that sympathetic innervation, which accompanies the BM vasculature, may regulate the endothelial stem cell niche, whether osteoblasts can influence the attraction of these stem cells in the BM is unknown.",
